(49405, 131238, 4537, 3, 'Rock', '', '2012-06-10 00:00:00', 2012, 0, 1, 7, '＜Rock＞\r\n詞：予樂\r\n曲+ 唱：Patricia Shih\r\n編曲+混音：于冠莛\r\n\r\nA1\r\nin the Geology class\r\n"name the three types of rock"\r\nIt''s a good question on my test\r\nWhat will you say?\r\nWhat will you say?\r\n\r\nA1\r\nin the Geology class\r\n"name the three types of rock"\r\nIt''s a good question on my test\r\nWhat will you say?\r\n\r\nB1\r\nwe have many types of rock\r\npebble, jadeite, olivine, marble even diamond\r\nNo matter which types\r\nthey have been polished a thousand million times\r\n\r\nB2\r\nwe have many types of rock\r\nclassic, punk, hard, metal and pop rock\r\nNo matter which types\r\nthey have been replaced a thousand million times\r\nC\r\nYes, you can see it\r\nwhat a pretty stone\r\nso you can listen to\r\nwhat a fantastic song\r\n\r\nB1(升KEY)\r\nwe have many types of rock\r\npebble, jadeite, olivine, marble even diamond\r\nNo matter which types\r\nthey have been polished a thousand million times\r\n\r\nB2\r\nwe have many types of rock\r\nclassic, punk, hard, metal and pop rock\r\nNo matter which types\r\nthey have been replaced a thousand million times\r\n\r\nA1 (慢)\r\nin the Geology class\r\n"name the three types of rock"\r\nIt''s a good question on my test\r\nWhat will you say?\r\nWhat will you say?\r\n\r\nA2(快)\r\n( COME ON!)\r\nin the Geology class\r\nlearn the three types of rock\r\nI''d like to play my rock \r\nI love my rockable life\r\nI love my rockable life\r\nI love my rockable life', '', 187, '', 'Patricia Shih', '予樂', '于冠莛', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-06-15 00:21:33', '2015-03-12 13:53:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
